notes.note: Starting late Sept., the course is at Belle Sherman Elementary (Mitchell Street). With clean-up and the commute back to campus, students probably would be back on campus at 3:10. However, if students have a 2:55 class, they are allowed to leave at 2:40 pm. Priority enrollment for students who will be first-years in Fall 2014. Contact Bryan Duff (bpd38) for more info and permission to enroll.

Students from all Colleges must submit a CALS Special Studies Form (Available online: http://cals.cornell.edu/academics/registrar/policies/#independent-study). Do not sign into section 601. You will be put in the course after submitting form online.
